settime0
========

settime0 is a wrapper for ntpdate(8). A symlink named settime pointing to the most recent version of settime should be placed in a directory that is in the PATH.

* read the list of NTP servers and their stats from the config file
* chose the NTP server(s) to query
* query the chosen NTP server(s) using ntpdate(8)
* update the stats

